<%= render "shared/header" %>

<div class="noise"></div>
<div class="cursor-glow" id="glow"></div>

<main>
  <section class="section internal-hero">
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">The Studio</div>
      <h1>We are a product lab focused on <span class="gold">immersion and engineering.</span></h1>
      <p class="lead" style="margin-top: 26px">Vanilla Labs was founded on the principle that the web should feel tactile, deep, and alive. We don't just build sites; we build digital artifacts that drive business growth.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-stats reveal">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">50+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Products Launched</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">12</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Core Lab Members</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">99.9%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">System Uptime</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">4</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Years of Craft</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-block reveal" style="max-width: 100%">
      <div style="border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid rgba(245, 230, 200, 0.1); margin: 60px 0;">
        <img src="/studio.png" alt="Vanilla Labs Studio" style="width: 100%; display: block; filter: saturate(0.8) contrast(1.1)">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-block reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">Our Story</div>
      <h2>Born from a <span class="gold">minimalist obsession.</span></h2>
      <p class="lead" style="margin-top: 20px">Starting in 2022 as a small infrastructure collective, Vanilla Labs evolved into a full-service production house. We realized that the most successful products aren't just functional—they are beautiful, fast, and emotionally resonant.</p>
      <p class="lead" style="margin-top: 20px; color: var(--muted)">We've spent the last four years refining a workflow that eliminates the friction between "the idea" and "the launch." By keeping our team small and our standards impossibly high, we ensure that every project receives the attention to detail it deserves.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-block reveal" style="margin-top: 100px; max-width: 100%;">
      <div class="eyebrow">Pillars</div>
      <h2>The <span class="gold">Vanilla Standards.</span></h2>
      
      <div class="pillar-grid">
        <div class="pillar-card">
          <span class="pillar-num">01 · MOTION</span>
          <div class="pillar-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Purposeful Motion</h3>
          <p>Animation isn't decoration. We use motion to guide the user's eye, provide feedback, and create a sense of physical weight and depth.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pillar-card">
          <span class="pillar-num">02 · INTEGRITY</span>
          <div class="pillar-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Technical Integrity</h3>
          <p>We build on rock-solid foundations. From Ruby on Rails to high-performance VPS clusters, our stack is chosen for long-term stability.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pillar-card">
          <span class="pillar-num">03 · DEPTH</span>
          <div class="pillar-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5"/><path d="M7 7h10v10H7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Design with Depth</h3>
          <p>We move beyond flat UI. Our designs utilize light, shadow, and layering to create "glassmorphic" interfaces that feel tangible.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-block reveal" style="margin-top: 120px;">
      <div class="eyebrow">The Lab</div>
      <h2>Engineering <span class="gold">without compromises.</span></h2>
      <p class="lead" style="margin-top: 20px">Our environment is our edge. We work in a high-focus "lab" setting where we experiment with new interaction models, 3D web technologies, and automation frameworks before deploying them to production.</p>
      <div class="btn-row" style="margin-top: 40px">
        <a href="/team" class="btn primary">Meet the people</a>
        <a href="/career" class="btn">Join the lab</a>
        <a href="/faq" class="btn">View FAQ</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%= render "shared/stack_showcase" %>

    <div class="content-block reveal" style="margin-top: 120px; max-width: 100%; overflow: hidden;">
      <div class="eyebrow" style="justify-content:center; margin-bottom: 30px">Impact</div>
      <h2 style="text-align:center">Trusted by <span class="gold">innovative founders.</span></h2>
      
      <div class="reviews-ticker">
        <div class="reviews-track">
          <!-- Cards -->
          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-stars">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <p class="review-text">"Vanilla Labs didn't just build our site; they built a brand experience. The 3D interactions and speed are unmatched."</p>
            <div class="review-author">
              <div class="author-avatar">JD</div>
              <div class="author-info"><h4>James Dalton</h4><span>CEO, Nebula Stream</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-stars">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <p class="review-text">"The level of technical depth they brought to our SaaS infrastructure was incredible. Truly a world-class team."</p>
            <div class="review-author">
              <div class="author-avatar">SC</div>
              <div class="author-info"><h4>Sarah Chen</h4><span>CTO, Pulse Logic</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-stars">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <p class="review-text">"They converted our complex legacy system into a sleek, performant dashboard in record time. Impeccable craft."</p>
            <div class="review-author">
              <div class="author-avatar">MK</div>
              <div class="author-info"><h4>Marcus Knight</h4><span>Founder, Orion CRM</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Repeat for Seamless Loop -->
          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-stars">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <p class="review-text">"Vanilla Labs didn't just build our site; they built a brand experience. The 3D interactions and speed are unmatched."</p>
            <div class="review-author">
              <div class="author-avatar">JD</div>
              <div class="author-info"><h4>James Dalton</h4><span>CEO, Nebula Stream</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta reveal" style="margin-top: 150px;">
      <div class="eyebrow" style="justify-content:center">Collaborate</div>
      <h2>Ready to build something <span class="gold">extraordinary?</span></h2>
      <p class="lead" style="margin: 20px auto 0">We are currently taking on new projects for Q3 and Q4 2026. Secure your spot in the lab today.</p>
      <div class="btn-row" style="justify-content:center">
        <a class="btn primary" href="mailto:hello@vanillalabs.io">hello@vanillalabs.io</a>
        <a class="btn" href="/#work">Explore our work</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%= render "shared/footer" %>
